{
  "video_id": "Ht40yrt3VrY",
  "title": "The Big Brexit Short",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 560.0,
      "end_time": 4439.0,
      "text": "Let June the 23rd go down in our history"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 4440.0,
      "end_time": 6960.0,
      "text": "as our independence day!"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 7160.0,
      "end_time": 8760.0,
      "text": "The British people have made a very"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 8760.0,
      "end_time": 12800.0,
      "text": "clear decision to take a different path."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 14400.0,
      "end_time": 18120.0,
      "text": "No one really knows what the future is going to look like."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 18120.0,
      "end_time": 20120.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s a defacement of the Union Jack!"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 20120.0,
      "end_time": 21640.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re not allowed to deface our flag"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 21640.0,
      "end_time": 24880.0,
      "text": "The shocking defeat of the Remain campaign,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 24880.0,
      "end_time": 26759.0,
      "text": "\"We&#39;ve got our country back\""
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 26760.0,
      "end_time": 29560.0,
      "text": "Caused the largest collapse of any major currency"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 29560.0,
      "end_time": 31919.0,
      "text": "in the history of the modern global financial system."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 31920.0,
      "end_time": 33880.0,
      "text": "You could literally watch the pound"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 33880.0,
      "end_time": 35960.0,
      "text": "falling off the edge of a cliff."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 35960.0,
      "end_time": 39160.0,
      "text": "The last time we saw falls of 8%,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 39160.0,
      "end_time": 40599.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not sure we actually know."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 40600.0,
      "end_time": 42800.0,
      "text": "People in the City of London were running"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 42800.0,
      "end_time": 45680.0,
      "text": "their own private polling to get information"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 45680.0,
      "end_time": 47400.0,
      "text": "about the vote while it was still happening."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 48480.0,
      "end_time": 50480.0,
      "text": "It was probably one of the most lucrative nights"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 50480.0,
      "end_time": 53160.0,
      "text": "for the hedge fund industry that there had ever been."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 57760.0,
      "end_time": 61239.0,
      "text": "My name&#39;s Gavin Finch, I&#39;m a journalist at Bloomberg News."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 61240.0,
      "end_time": 63480.0,
      "text": "I cover financial crime."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 63480.0,
      "end_time": 67679.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m Cam Simpson, I&#39;m an investigations editor and writer."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 68720.0,
      "end_time": 70120.0,
      "text": "My name is Kit Chellel,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 70120.0,
      "end_time": 71440.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m a reporter with Bloomberg,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 71440.0,
      "end_time": 73520.0,
      "text": "and a writer for Businessweek."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 73520.0,
      "end_time": 74880.0,
      "text": "And we&#39;re the three reporters"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 74880.0,
      "end_time": 77440.0,
      "text": "who broke the Brexit Big Short."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 78120.0,
      "end_time": 79320.0,
      "text": "The Brexit night was a huge deal"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 79320.0,
      "end_time": 80720.0,
      "text": "for everyone in the country."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 80720.0,
      "end_time": 83920.0,
      "text": "I watched it on television the same way most people did."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 83920.0,
      "end_time": 86400.0,
      "text": "At 10pm voting stopped,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 86400.0,
      "end_time": 87600.0,
      "text": "the polling stations closed."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 87600.0,
      "end_time": 90440.0,
      "text": "All of the networks, all of the broadcasters"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 90440.0,
      "end_time": 92320.0,
      "text": "went immediately to their coverage."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 93440.0,
      "end_time": 96880.0,
      "text": "In or out. It is too late to change your mind now."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 97240.0,
      "end_time": 101560.0,
      "text": "So within the first minute they had a concession"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 101560.0,
      "end_time": 105120.0,
      "text": "from Nigel Farage who&#39;s the global face of Brexit."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 105120.0,
      "end_time": 107880.0,
      "text": "This statement, as the polls close,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 107880.0,
      "end_time": 110240.0,
      "text": "\"It&#39;s been an extraordinary referendum campaign,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 110240.0,
      "end_time": 112000.0,
      "text": "this is Nigel Farage, \"turnout looks to be"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 112000.0,
      "end_time": 115960.0,
      "text": "exceptionally high and looks like Remain will edge it.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 115960.0,
      "end_time": 119279.0,
      "text": "I remember being shocked when I heard that just"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 119280.0,
      "end_time": 122560.0,
      "text": "because it was quite out of character for somebody like him"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 122560.0,
      "end_time": 126480.0,
      "text": "to concede before even the results had been counted."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 126480.0,
      "end_time": 128440.0,
      "text": "Later that evening, Nigel Farage came"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 128440.0,
      "end_time": 130440.0,
      "text": "out again with a second concession speech,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 130440.0,
      "end_time": 132720.0,
      "text": "and this one was a bit more specific than the first."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 132720.0,
      "end_time": 136800.0,
      "text": "In this one he said that Remain had won,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 136800.0,
      "end_time": 139440.0,
      "text": "and that he had heard this from some friends"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 139440.0,
      "end_time": 142200.0,
      "text": "in the City who run some pretty big private polling."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 142200.0,
      "end_time": 144160.0,
      "text": "And that really shook me."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 144160.0,
      "end_time": 146520.0,
      "text": "That was when I really realized, wait a minute."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 147440.0,
      "end_time": 151840.0,
      "text": "The pollsters secretly working with hedge funds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 151840.0,
      "end_time": 154880.0,
      "text": "and Nigel had access  to that information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 154880.0,
      "end_time": 158560.0,
      "text": "before any of the votes were even announced."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 158560.0,
      "end_time": 161200.0,
      "text": "That was the moment when I realized"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 161200.0,
      "end_time": 164239.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s a lot here for us to look into."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 166800.0,
      "end_time": 169400.0,
      "text": "First thing that I did was I created a very detailed"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 169400.0,
      "end_time": 172000.0,
      "text": "timeline of everything that happened politically,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 172000.0,
      "end_time": 173480.0,
      "text": "everything that the pollsters were doing"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 173480.0,
      "end_time": 175320.0,
      "text": "and how the markets were reacting."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 175320.0,
      "end_time": 177720.0,
      "text": "We had to try to identify the polling firms that were"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 177720.0,
      "end_time": 180200.0,
      "text": "involved and the hedge funds that they were working for."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 180200.0,
      "end_time": 182799.0,
      "text": "So we had these two giant haystacks"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 182800.0,
      "end_time": 185720.0,
      "text": "that we kinda had to go searching for needles in."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 185720.0,
      "end_time": 188000.0,
      "text": "We call this a mosaic investigation."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 188000.0,
      "end_time": 190120.0,
      "text": "You gather all the pieces that you can"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 190120.0,
      "end_time": 191320.0,
      "text": "and you build a mosaic."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 191320.0,
      "end_time": 194239.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not a perfect picture, but it&#39;s a good picture"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 194240.0,
      "end_time": 197360.0,
      "text": "and one that you can kind of see what happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 197360.0,
      "end_time": 201720.0,
      "text": "So we set out to interview as many"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 201720.0,
      "end_time": 204200.0,
      "text": "of the polling company employees,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 204200.0,
      "end_time": 205839.0,
      "text": "former employees we started with"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 205840.0,
      "end_time": 207880.0,
      "text": "so as not to alert them to what we were doing."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 207880.0,
      "end_time": 211200.0,
      "text": "And people were genuinely scared about the implications"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 211200.0,
      "end_time": 213320.0,
      "text": "of talking to a journalist about something like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 213320.0,
      "end_time": 215280.0,
      "text": "We basically wanted to know who the buyers were"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 215280.0,
      "end_time": 218480.0,
      "text": "of these polls and who was conducting them and why."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 219920.0,
      "end_time": 222640.0,
      "text": "Two polling firms that were notable in all this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 222640.0,
      "end_time": 225790.0,
      "text": "and that we highlighted in the story,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 225800.0,
      "end_time": 228000.0,
      "text": "were YouGov which is one of the fastest-growing"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 228000.0,
      "end_time": 229960.0,
      "text": "polling companies in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 229960.0,
      "end_time": 232520.0,
      "text": "and a company called Survation."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 235800.0,
      "end_time": 238000.0,
      "text": "Hello and welcome to Pop Idol."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 238000.0,
      "end_time": 242120.0,
      "text": "In the early stages of both YouGov and Survation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 242120.0,
      "end_time": 244840.0,
      "text": "part of their market legend was built around the work"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 244840.0,
      "end_time": 248840.0,
      "text": "they did on U.K. talent competitions"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 248840.0,
      "end_time": 251480.0,
      "text": "like Pop Idol and X Factor."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 255440.0,
      "end_time": 259640.0,
      "text": "They were really the first to build polling panels,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 259640.0,
      "end_time": 263390.0,
      "text": "large groups of people that were available to them online"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 263400.0,
      "end_time": 265160.0,
      "text": "that they could tap with sort of the press of a button."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 265160.0,
      "end_time": 268800.0,
      "text": "What was interesting about those polls"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 268800.0,
      "end_time": 271120.0,
      "text": "is it was an early indicator that you didn&#39;t need to know"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 271120.0,
      "end_time": 274240.0,
      "text": "the outcome of the actual competition."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 274240.0,
      "end_time": 276480.0,
      "text": "You didn&#39;t need to know who won X Factor."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 276480.0,
      "end_time": 279320.0,
      "text": "All you needed to know was who was gonna vote"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 279320.0,
      "end_time": 283240.0,
      "text": "for which candidate on which particular week in X Factor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 283240.0,
      "end_time": 286200.0,
      "text": "for you to then be able to make a market bet."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 290280.0,
      "end_time": 292400.0,
      "text": "For the Brexit referendum, the senior members"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 292400.0,
      "end_time": 295679.0,
      "text": "of the polling industry told the press that it was not"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 295680.0,
      "end_time": 300400.0,
      "text": "possible to do a regular exit poll for this event."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 300400.0,
      "end_time": 302000.0,
      "text": "Their normal methods, their normal data gathering"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 302000.0,
      "end_time": 304640.0,
      "text": "simply wouldn&#39;t work in this context."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 304640.0,
      "end_time": 306440.0,
      "text": "What they didn&#39;t say was they were secretly"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 306440.0,
      "end_time": 309400.0,
      "text": "doing it for hedge funds  at the same time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 309400.0,
      "end_time": 312799.0,
      "text": "who were trying to  profit on the day"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 312800.0,
      "end_time": 314760.0,
      "text": "from the ultimate inside information"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 314760.0,
      "end_time": 318000.0,
      "text": "which was an exit poll showing how British people had voted."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 322000.0,
      "end_time": 322960.0,
      "text": "Hedge funds are among the"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 322960.0,
      "end_time": 326599.0,
      "text": "most sophisticated players in financial markets."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 326600.0,
      "end_time": 327960.0,
      "text": "What they&#39;re looking for is an edge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 327960.0,
      "end_time": 330159.0,
      "text": "some sort of insight that no one else has"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 330160.0,
      "end_time": 333800.0,
      "text": "that they can use to make their trading profits"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 333800.0,
      "end_time": 334359.0,
      "text": "and make money for their investors."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 334520.0,
      "end_time": 336719.0,
      "text": "If the markets were deciding this referendum,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 336720.0,
      "end_time": 339480.0,
      "text": "they would already have called it for Remain."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 339480.0,
      "end_time": 342200.0,
      "text": "The pound is absolutely surging on the markets."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 342280.0,
      "end_time": 344239.0,
      "text": "But the pound kept going to new highs"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 344240.0,
      "end_time": 345680.0,
      "text": "all throughout the evening."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 345680.0,
      "end_time": 349360.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re a hedge fund with access to information"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 349360.0,
      "end_time": 353240.0,
      "text": "showing you that actually, the opposite is likely to happen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 353240.0,
      "end_time": 355360.0,
      "text": "then you&#39;re in an incredibly good place"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 355360.0,
      "end_time": 359000.0,
      "text": "because you can play that market all the way up to the top."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 359000.0,
      "end_time": 362400.0,
      "text": "Short selling is essentially a bet in a given direction."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 362400.0,
      "end_time": 364320.0,
      "text": "The bet is that something will fall in value."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 364320.0,
      "end_time": 366320.0,
      "text": "So the higher the pound is pushed up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 366320.0,
      "end_time": 367719.0,
      "text": "the more money you make when it"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 367720.0,
      "end_time": 370000.0,
      "text": "comes back down the other side."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 370000.0,
      "end_time": 371720.0,
      "text": "Hedge funds and banks were willing to pay"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 371720.0,
      "end_time": 374480.0,
      "text": "comparatively enormous  sums for the data"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 374480.0,
      "end_time": 376240.0,
      "text": "that polling firms were selling"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 376240.0,
      "end_time": 378640.0,
      "text": "because it allowed them to trade so profitably."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 378640.0,
      "end_time": 381360.0,
      "text": "$100 million, $160 million,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 381360.0,
      "end_time": 384400.0,
      "text": "$300 million in a single day."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 385200.0,
      "end_time": 388120.0,
      "text": "When you&#39;re looking at the definition of insider trading,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 388120.0,
      "end_time": 391520.0,
      "text": "insider trading is when you have access to"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 391520.0,
      "end_time": 396599.0,
      "text": "and trade on non-public, market-moving information."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 396600.0,
      "end_time": 398880.0,
      "text": "In this country, exit polling data is"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 398880.0,
      "end_time": 401680.0,
      "text": "criminally defined as non-public information."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 401680.0,
      "end_time": 404480.0,
      "text": "It is a crime to provide it to the public"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 404480.0,
      "end_time": 408360.0,
      "text": "or any section of the public before the polls are closed."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 408360.0,
      "end_time": 410560.0,
      "text": "Polling companies were streaming it all day long"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 410560.0,
      "end_time": 412720.0,
      "text": "to their secret hedge fund clients"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 412720.0,
      "end_time": 414560.0,
      "text": "long before the polls were closed"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 414560.0,
      "end_time": 416440.0,
      "text": "so that they could trade on how people"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 416440.0,
      "end_time": 419160.0,
      "text": "were voting while they were still voting."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 419960.0,
      "end_time": 424390.0,
      "text": "I hope and pray that my sense of this tonight is wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 424400.0,
      "end_time": 425600.0,
      "text": "Nigel Farage does seem to think"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 425600.0,
      "end_time": 427480.0,
      "text": "that the referendum is lost."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 427480.0,
      "end_time": 429920.0,
      "text": "The results as they&#39;ve been coming through this evening,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 429920.0,
      "end_time": 434320.0,
      "text": "rather I think cast doubt, very early stage, on Mr. Farage&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 434320.0,
      "end_time": 436960.0,
      "text": "rather low-key approach to what&#39;s going on."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 436960.0,
      "end_time": 440120.0,
      "text": "So on the evening of the Brexit vote"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 440120.0,
      "end_time": 441440.0,
      "text": "after the markets had closed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 441440.0,
      "end_time": 446360.0,
      "text": "the concession speeches which Nigel gave"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 446400.0,
      "end_time": 448919.0,
      "text": "certainly did drive markets higher."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 448920.0,
      "end_time": 451760.0,
      "text": "What we wanted to understand was"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 451760.0,
      "end_time": 453760.0,
      "text": "why did he concede that night?"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 453760.0,
      "end_time": 456680.0,
      "text": "What information did he have when he made those concessions?"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 456680.0,
      "end_time": 458800.0,
      "text": "What was going through his mind?"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 458800.0,
      "end_time": 462000.0,
      "text": "And whether he had access to some of the private polling"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 462000.0,
      "end_time": 464760.0,
      "text": "that we had identified that was being done by hedge funds?"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 464760.0,
      "end_time": 467920.0,
      "text": "So we really had to figure out a way to try"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 467960.0,
      "end_time": 469320.0,
      "text": "and get to the bottom of some of this"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 469320.0,
      "end_time": 472880.0,
      "text": "and we asked Nigel to come to lunch with us."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 475360.0,
      "end_time": 478640.0,
      "text": "So we met Nigel Farge at Sweetings."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 478640.0,
      "end_time": 480640.0,
      "text": "That was on Kit&#39;s suggestion"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 480640.0,
      "end_time": 482440.0,
      "text": "and it was a good one because it turns out that"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 482440.0,
      "end_time": 485840.0,
      "text": "Nigel was the third generation of his family"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 485840.0,
      "end_time": 487640.0,
      "text": "who had been eating at Sweetings."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 489840.0,
      "end_time": 491400.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s kind of a strange venue."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 491400.0,
      "end_time": 494159.0,
      "text": "It feels like stepping back into the 1950s."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 494160.0,
      "end_time": 496960.0,
      "text": "We went in through the door with him."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 496960.0,
      "end_time": 498799.0,
      "text": "And he immediately had a go at the"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 498800.0,
      "end_time": 502120.0,
      "text": "Spanish host and waiter for being Spanish."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 502200.0,
      "end_time": 504560.0,
      "text": "I&#39;d never eaten oysters before,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 504560.0,
      "end_time": 507720.0,
      "text": "and Nigel Farage insisted that I try oysters."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 508560.0,
      "end_time": 511120.0,
      "text": "About halfway through the meal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 511120.0,
      "end_time": 515560.0,
      "text": "our attention certainly changed to our story."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 515558.99999999994,
      "end_time": 518558.99999999994,
      "text": "And we started asking him about his concession speeches."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 518558.99999999994,
      "end_time": 521118.99999999994,
      "text": "If we&#39;d just tried to call him up and ask those questions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 521120.0,
      "end_time": 522480.0,
      "text": "he would have hung up the phone."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 522480.0,
      "end_time": 524880.0,
      "text": "Or if we knocked on his door, he would have shut the door."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 524880.0,
      "end_time": 528800.0,
      "text": "But he felt, I think, compelled at that point"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 528800.0,
      "end_time": 532240.0,
      "text": "to give us full answers and we got them."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 534640.0,
      "end_time": 539480.0,
      "text": "He certainly confirmed to us that in between"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 539480.0,
      "end_time": 541800.0,
      "text": "at least the beginning of the first concession"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 541800.0,
      "end_time": 544439.0,
      "text": "and the second concession, he had spoken to"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 544440.0,
      "end_time": 546840.0,
      "text": "Damien Lyons Lowe at Survation."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 546840.0,
      "end_time": 549960.0,
      "text": "Damien Lyons Lowe is the founder and the CEO of Survation."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 549960.0,
      "end_time": 553160.0,
      "text": "He built Survation&#39;s reputation in the early days"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 553160.0,
      "end_time": 558160.0,
      "text": "by polling in a way that drove UKIP&#39;s results higher."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 558520.0,
      "end_time": 559800.0,
      "text": "That immediately brought him"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 559800.0,
      "end_time": 561439.0,
      "text": "to the attention of Nigel Farage"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 561440.0,
      "end_time": 565200.0,
      "text": "and he became Nigel Farage&#39;s pollster and UKIP&#39;s pollster,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 565200.0,
      "end_time": 568000.0,
      "text": "and a very key political advisor for Nigel Farage."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 568000.0,
      "end_time": 572800.0,
      "text": "Nigel knew from his favorite pollster"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 572800.0,
      "end_time": 574480.0,
      "text": "Leave had won before he gave at least"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 574480.0,
      "end_time": 576920.0,
      "text": "one of his concessions that really pushed the"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 576920.0,
      "end_time": 578920.0,
      "text": "market in the wrong direction that night."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 578920.0,
      "end_time": 581160.0,
      "text": "So that was pretty critical for us to find out."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 581160.0,
      "end_time": 584120.0,
      "text": "On the night that he gave the concession speech,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 584120.0,
      "end_time": 587240.0,
      "text": "we do know there were others within UKIP and"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 587240.0,
      "end_time": 592960.0,
      "text": "within the Leave EU campaign who were very curious"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 592960.0,
      "end_time": 593000.0,
      "text": "within the Leave EU campaign who were very curious as to why he was going on air saying that Leave had lost"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 593000.0,
      "end_time": 599320.0,
      "text": "as to why he was going on air saying that Leave had lost"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 599320.0,
      "end_time": 602960.0,
      "text": "because they too had access to this private polling data"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 602960.0,
      "end_time": 603920.0,
      "text": "which showed that Leave had won."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 604720.0,
      "end_time": 608160.0,
      "text": "The reasons he gave to us that he made those concessions"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 608160.0,
      "end_time": 611800.0,
      "text": "were simply that he had an attack of nerves, essentially."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 611800.0,
      "end_time": 614120.0,
      "text": "When the moment came he got jittery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 614120.0,
      "end_time": 615480.0,
      "text": "and nervous, and lost faith."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 615480.0,
      "end_time": 619280.0,
      "text": "He described being in a sort of black despair and a gloom"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 619280.0,
      "end_time": 622760.0,
      "text": "about what the outcome would be and losing hope."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 622760.0,
      "end_time": 624520.0,
      "text": "What his personal dealings were"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 624520.0,
      "end_time": 628400.0,
      "text": "we&#39;re not sure of but we&#39;re still looking."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 629480.0,
      "end_time": 632120.0,
      "text": "This whole process was us building"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 632120.0,
      "end_time": 634480.0,
      "text": "a very complicated jigsaw from scratch"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 634480.0,
      "end_time": 636200.0,
      "text": "and it perhaps wasn&#39;t right until the end"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 636200.0,
      "end_time": 638720.0,
      "text": "of the reporting process that we really saw"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 638720.0,
      "end_time": 641800.0,
      "text": "the whole picture in all its complexity."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 641800.0,
      "end_time": 642440.0,
      "text": "The fallout was massive."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 642440.0,
      "end_time": 644760.0,
      "text": "I mean we were really surprised that a story about"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 644760.0,
      "end_time": 647840.0,
      "text": "derivatives, essentially, was like"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 647840.0,
      "end_time": 650320.0,
      "text": "the third biggest trending thing on Twitter."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 650320.0,
      "end_time": 655000.0,
      "text": "And it didn&#39;t take long  for U.K. lawmakers"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 655000.0,
      "end_time": 658600.0,
      "text": "in both Houses of Parliament to start calling"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 658600.0,
      "end_time": 661800.0,
      "text": "for official inquiries into this."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 661560.0,
      "end_time": 664400.0,
      "text": "It matters to different people for different reasons."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 664400.0,
      "end_time": 666640.0,
      "text": "It matters if you&#39;re a trader because it matters"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 666640.0,
      "end_time": 669400.0,
      "text": "if someone else has an unfair advantage over you."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 669400.0,
      "end_time": 672480.0,
      "text": "It matters if you care that a handful of people"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 672480.0,
      "end_time": 678200.0,
      "text": "can make huge sums of money by betting on political events"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 678200.0,
      "end_time": 681760.0,
      "text": "that shape our future and using information that would be"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 681760.0,
      "end_time": 683800.0,
      "text": "illegal for you or I to look at."
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 683800.0,
      "end_time": 687800.0,
      "text": "I think it matters if politicians are involved in this"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 687800.0,
      "end_time": 689839.0,
      "text": "and we should know more about it."
    }
  ]
}